webcam should rec all the number plates and update in the database, so if any vehicle gets lost we can search for that number we can see the signals through with the vehicle is passed. 8 signals are placed and 8 are connected to the esp. only four signal has webcam. because its prototype
  its a smart traffic system . its idealogy is to find the ambulance detection if the ambulance is detected in the signal that signal alone opens others are closed en suring the traffic free way for ambulance, another is signal light based onvehicle count. normally the timer is set in static im maing this changing based on the number of vehicles present in signal, another is for collision if there is a accident detect in cam or entered in the dashboard the signal so that the route is diverted to another. im using four webcam placed in the 4 signal, and esp 8266 for signal control and blynk to operate signal manually if required. see all these files in my github

